ActPublic Service Labour Relations and Employment Board Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Works and Government Services to be the Minister referred to in the Act
PrecisOrder (a) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2014-912 of August 15, 2014; and (b) designating the MINISTER OF PUBLIC WORKS AND GOVERNMENT SERVICES, who is not a member of the Treasury Board, to be the MINISTER referred to in the PUBLIC SERVICE LABOUR RELATIONS AND EMPLOYMENT BOARD ACT, effective November 4, 2015.
